{
  "doc_id": "40825",
  "text": "For tree growing, we adopted a C++ implementation of C4.5 Release 8 [CITATION_1] . The parametric simplification algorithm proposed in this paper was developed on top of it, with all source code written in standard C++. Elapsed times reported in the paper consider only the tree simplification phase, not tree growing. They refer to a common PC desktop architecture: Xeon 5150 @2.66GHz 4MB L2 cache and 2 GBytes of main memory, with Linux x86 64 2.6.18.",
