  "bib_entries": {
    "13418055": {
      "title": "YaDT: Yet another Decision tree Builder",
      "abstract": "YaDT is a from-scratch main-memory implementation of the C4.5-like decision tree algorithm. Our presentation would be focused on the design principles that allowed for obtaining an extremely efficient system. Experimental results are reported comparing YaDT with Weka, dti, Xelopes and (E)C4.5."
